## WHITELOTTO DEV CRON

# every hour update lottery
0 * * * * /usr/bin/wget -4 -q --spider https://empire.whitelotto.loc/task/lotteryupdate
# send e-mail notifications after draw
* * * * * /usr/bin/wget -4 -q --spider https://empire.whitelotto.loc/task/drawnotification
# every day at noon check for lottery draw changes
0 12 * * * /usr/bin/wget -4 -q --spider https://empire.whitelotto.loc/task/check_superenalotto_delay
5 12 * * * sudo -H -u www-data FUEL_ENV="production" php /var/www/whitelotto/platform/oil r sync_draws >> /dev/null 2>&1

